title: LoL Puns?
body: I've got a Zilean. Ask Annie-one, they'll confirm it. Come on, don't make that face. I'm Naut that cheezey, am I? It's quite the Miss Fortune that more people can't appreciate jokes like these. I mean, I'm not trying to Vi for attention here, and I don't mean to sound Vayne, it's just that my THRESHold for boredom is quite low, so I thought I would make this thread.
